HR NO. 198 ENROLLED
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Karaline Elizabeth Leblanc for being named
the 2026 Breaux Bridge Crawfish Festival Queen and does hereby extend sincere wishes that
she remains prosperous in all of her endeavors.
